description: A McMullen transform involving x->x+1/x of Lehmer's polynomial gives the polynomial used to get this expansion sequence: p(x)=1 + x + 10 x^2 + 8 x^3 + 44 x^4 + 28 x^5 + 113 x^6 + 57 x^7 + 191 x^8 + 79 x^9 + 227 x^10 + 79 x^11 + 191 x^12 + 57 x^13 + 113 x^14 + 28 x^15 + 44 x^16 + 8 x^17 + 10 x^18 + x^19 + x^20.
